{"name": "Concord Baptist Church", "alternate_name": "", "description": "* Hours open: the 4th Friday of each month from 10 am until food is gone .
* For pantry  distribution day for months of November and December please call the church to confirm date.
* We are primarily a drive through facility ,however we do accept walkers.
* We do not ask for proof of address or provide clothing.
* Pantry is only closed month of August .
* We provide groceries including meats.
* All are welcome.
* Please call church for any questions.
	* 410-367-1117
	* Food Pantry Coordinator
	* Patricia Brockington
